Generate first hit the big apple back in June 2014, and has enjoyed 4 fantastic conferences to date.

With previous speakers including Mike Monteiro, Karen McGrane, Brad Frost, Sara Soueidan and Dan Mall, Generate New York has always strived to provide the industry with top speakers from around the world. Topics covering the very latest developments in animation, CSS, accessibility, as well as inspiring talks to help you achieve more.
